806
00:35:01,030 --> 00:35:02,200
Don't you, Lin?

807
00:35:02,230 --> 00:35:04,370
Pam, I'm not
disagreeing with you.

808
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:06,130
Please believe me.
I'm on your side.

809
00:35:06,170 --> 00:35:07,870
I know that
there's something there.

810
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:10,800
I'm just trying to understand
