847
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:39,870
You can't. You've got to
get out of the lab
and into real life,

848
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:43,070
and that's what we're trying
to do tonight.

849
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:46,700
These people are not
deceiving us or themselves.
